{
  "stem": "1062.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So everybody want to stay on top, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But this was-- but in Buna already it was different.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Buna, there was already bathrooms, more or less.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in-- in-- in-- in-- in-- in there was one place where they had showers, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Once a week we go for showers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You could go for delousing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Delousing is you took off your clothes and you throw them in there, and-- and they boiled-- they boiled-- you know, they-- they boiled the-- the clothes.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they gave them back to you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'll tell you one thing-- in Auschwitz, in Buna, there were no lice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, there were no-- you know, there was no-- they-- they kept pretty clean there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The only problem is, you know, in Buna, whenever after a couple of weeks, they would come there for a selection.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In other words, there was come a doctor-- this doctor's name was, in Buna, his name was-- his name was Fisher.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they would take the whole block and line 'em up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And whoever was too skinny, you know, they would take them out in the night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And a couple of days later, they were sent to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My uncle was sent there, and other-- you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And even there, I remember even there, when they-- when they-- when they had a selection to take them away to Auschwitz, and there was a rumor they're going to be gassed.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there was one boy I knew, he says to me, they're going to go to a sanatorium in order to build us up a little bit.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Even then they wouldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right, let me tell you--in Buna, no, I did not know there were gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
